just simple vwap touch entry to test out on different time frames with adjustable TP/Sl. I like to do the limit order entry based off previous candle close keeps it mechanical. thats why you see 2 vwaps the current one which is alwasy moving like a normal vwap the other if the previous candle close vwap level. I use that to trail limit orders. I have an Ema touch Indicator that works the same way
